Niki Shisler A British mother tells us about the agonising choice she and her husband faced following the birth of their severely disabled son. '89 Squared We hear from Revolution Square in Bucharest about the year Communism came to an end in Romania. Tuareg Rebel Martin Vogl reports from Mali where he meets a former Tuareg rebel trying to build a better future for himself. Show less